{
  "stem": "6258.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You never, during the Second World War, when you were Jewish, and when you were Polish, you never asked a German why do they execute people?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they want to, period.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because obviously, at this time, they could not-- at-- at this time, they needed us badly in the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if not, they would go on the front to Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, of course, glance or not glance, or because of this or because of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever you did or whatever you didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes we're-- say we're in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the SS were absolutely you know, free.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anytime, they could go into the barrack or into the latrine or into this and that and shoot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When there was-- when they found that someone had smuggled something, then they  shoot everybody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they found-- it was not like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was-- It is very difficult to answer, because this question seems so naive to the reality that was there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw once when there was--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Any--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know why you ask, because you are a logical person, and you are trying desperately to find a logical reason between this, what had absolutely no logic.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No morality, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, just nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, a friend of mine who is still in Krakow, he was so young at this time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the men were working outside and taking some difficult things and whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, they-- it was hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they took the jackets or sweaters and told him, you take care of this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Watch that nobody would steal it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was doing this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Amon Goth, the commander, he was watching through the binoculars from his seat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he noticed that there is someone sitting.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
